actions.name: AcceptDomainTransferFromAnotherAwsAccount
actions.description: Grants permission to accept the transfer of a domain from another AWS account to the current AWS account

actions.name: CancelDomainTransferToAnotherAwsAccount
actions.description: Grants permission to cancel the transfer of a domain from the current AWS account to another AWS account

actions.name: CheckDomainAvailability
actions.description: Grants permission to check the availability of one domain name

actions.name: CheckDomainTransferability
actions.description: Grants permission to check whether a domain name can be transferred to Amazon Route 53

actions.name: DeleteDomain
actions.description: Grants permission to delete domains

actions.name: DeleteTagsForDomain
actions.description: Grants permission to delete the specified tags for a domain

actions.name: DisableDomainAutoRenew
actions.description: Grants permission to configure Amazon Route 53 to automatically renew the specified domain before the domain registration expires

actions.name: DisableDomainTransferLock
actions.description: Grants permission to remove the transfer lock on the domain (specifically the clientTransferProhibited status) to allow domain transfers

actions.name: EnableDomainAutoRenew
actions.description: Grants permission to configure Amazon Route 53 to automatically renew the specified domain before the domain registration expires

actions.name: EnableDomainTransferLock
actions.description: Grants permission to set the transfer lock on the domain (specifically the clientTransferProhibited status) to prevent domain transfers

actions.name: GetContactReachabilityStatus
actions.description: Grants permission to get information about whether the registrant contact has responded for operations that require confirmation that the email address for the registrant contact is valid, such as registering a new domain

actions.name: GetDomainDetail
actions.description: Grants permission to get detailed information about a domain

actions.name: GetDomainSuggestions
actions.description: Grants permission to get a list of suggested domain names given a string, which can either be a domain name or simply a word or phrase (without spaces)

actions.name: GetOperationDetail
actions.description: Grants permission to get the current status of an operation that is not completed

actions.name: ListDomains
actions.description: Grants permission to list all the domain names registered with Amazon Route 53 for the current AWS account

actions.name: ListOperations
actions.description: Grants permission to list the operation IDs of operations that are not yet complete

actions.name: ListPrices
actions.description: Grants permission to list the prices of operations for TLDs

actions.name: ListTagsForDomain
actions.description: Grants permission to list all the tags that are associated with the specified domain

actions.name: RegisterDomain
actions.description: Grants permission to register domains

actions.name: RejectDomainTransferFromAnotherAwsAccount
actions.description: Grants permission to reject the transfer of a domain from another AWS account to the current AWS account

actions.name: RenewDomain
actions.description: Grants permission to renew domains for the specified number of years

actions.name: ResendContactReachabilityEmail
actions.description: Grants permission to resend the confirmation email to the current email address for the registrant contact for operations that require confirmation that the email address for the registrant contact is valid, such as registering a new domain

actions.name: RetrieveDomainAuthCode
actions.description: Grants permission to get the AuthCode for the domain

actions.name: TransferDomain
actions.description: Grants permission to transfer a domain from another registrar to Amazon Route 53

actions.name: TransferDomainToAnotherAwsAccount
actions.description: Grants permission to transfer a domain from the current AWS account to another AWS account

actions.name: UpdateDomainContact
actions.description: Grants permission to update the contact information for domain

actions.name: UpdateDomainContactPrivacy
actions.description: Grants permission to update the domain contact privacy setting

actions.name: UpdateDomainNameservers
actions.description: Grants permission to replace the current set of name servers for a domain with the specified set of name servers

actions.name: UpdateTagsForDomain
actions.description: Grants permission to add or update tags for a specified domain

actions.name: ViewBilling
actions.description: Grants permission to get all the domain-related billing records for the current AWS account for a specified period
